screen_desc: The screenshot shows a ride-hailing app interface where the user can reserve a ride. The interface includes fields for entering the "Pickup Location" and "Destination." There is a section labeled "Saved places" with an entry for "INTERLINK CORPORATION" located at "47 Đ. Điện Biên Phủ, Đa Kao, Quận 1, Hồ Chí..." and an option to "Set location on map." The keyboard at the bottom of the screen is active, displaying a custom background with a night sky and a tent. The time displayed at the top of the screen is 8:50 AM, and various status icons are visible, including battery, signal strength, and notifications.
